WEBVTT

00:06:58.640 --> 00:07:01.936
There's a group of people
that they call engaged workaholics.

00:07:01.960 --> 00:07:03.160
Is that you?

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:05.576
AH: Oh, I love it.

00:07:05.600 --> 00:07:07.336
I absolutely 100 percent love it.

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:10.440
I don't really have a distinction
between my work and my life.

00:07:11.200 --> 00:07:17.920
But I love it much more
when I have taken time to recharge.

00:07:18.520 --> 00:07:21.816
NR: I grew up listening
to stories about work.

00:07:21.840 --> 00:07:28.776
I grew up thinking that
it was really normal to talk about work,

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:31.936
to have these workplace conversations
at the dinner table.